HEADWORD: Domeykite
<hw>Do"mey*kite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Named after
<ets>Domeyko</ets>, a mineralogist of Chili.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld>
<def>A massive mineral of tin-white or steel-gray color, an arsenide of
copper.</def>⟦br⟧
